# Node ID

## Definition

A Node ID uniquely identifies a Node.

## Specification

Every Node MUST define exactly one Node ID.

A Node ID MUST be globally unique inside a Graph.

A Node ID MUST NOT depend on:

- filename
- directory
- repository location

References between Nodes SHALL use Node IDs.

Duplicate Node IDs MUST fail validation.

## Example

```
id: payment-authorization
```
